            153.00003051757812
          ],
          "text": "RBI/DCM/2018-19/63  \nMaster Direction DCM (CC) No.G-3/03.41.01/2018-19  \n July 3, 2018",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            172.7279815673828,
            282.7572937011719,
            220.44003295898438
          ],
          "text": "The Chairman and Managing Director / \nChief Executive Officers, \nAll Banks",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            234.8880157470703,
            172.71600341796875,
            250.86001586914062
          ],
          "text": "Madam / Dear Sir,",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            266.54400634765625,
            552.3400268554688,
            299.1120300292969
          ],
          "text": "Master Direction on Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES) based on \nperformance in rendering customer service to the members of public",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            314.993896484375,
            552.3423461914062,
            410.87994384765625
          ],
          "text": "In terms of the Preamble, under Section 45 of the RBI Act, 1934 and 35 A of the Banking \nRegulation Act, 1949, the Bank issues guidelines / instructions for realising the objectives \nof our Clean Note Policy. With a view to sustaining these objectives, the Bank has \nformulated a scheme of incentives titled Currency Distribution and Exchange Scheme \n(CDES) in order to ensure that all bank branches provide better customer services to \nmembers of public.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            431.4479675292969,
            549.0169677734375,
            479.1599426269531
          ],
          "text": "2. The Master Direction enclosed incorporates updated guidelines / circulars on the\nsubject. The Direction will be updated from time to time as and when fresh instructions\nare issued.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            500.0279846191406,
            467.49603271484375,
            516.0
          ],
          "text": "3. This Master Direction has been placed on RBI website at www.rbi.org.in.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            542.387939453125,
            157.416015625,
            558.3599853515625
          ],
          "text": "Yours faithfully,",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            599.2679443359375,
            210.0360107421875,
            629.0400390625
          ],
          "text": "(Manas Ranjan Mohanty) \nChief General Manager",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            639.5279541015625,
            155.37600708007812,
            655.5
          ],
          "text": "Encl: As above",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
