    {
      "page_number": 2,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            34.943973541259766,
            552.3359985351562,
            65.47196197509766
          ],
          "text": "Annex",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            72.62396240234375,
            552.3399047851562,
            121.0920181274414
          ],
          "text": "Circular on “Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES)” for bank branches \nincluding currency chests based on performance in rendering customer service to \nmembers of public",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            130.16400146484375,
            552.3411254882812,
            193.86007690429688
          ],
          "text": "1. The Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES) for bank branches including \ncurrency chests has been formulated in order to ensure that all bank branches provide \nbetter customer service to members of public with regard to exchange of notes and coins, \nin keeping with the objectives of Clean Note Policy.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            203.60406494140625,
            153.99600219726562,
            220.33206176757812
          ],
          "text": "2.  Incentives",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.00000762939453,
            231.64808654785156,
            552.3397827148438,
            263.4601135253906
          ],
          "text": "As per the scheme, banks are eligible for the following financial incentives for providing \nfacilities for exchange of notes and coins:",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            80.27999877929688,
            275.7239990234375,
            102.93599700927734,
            306.2519836425781
          ],
          "text": "Sr. \nNo.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            157.8000030517578,
            275.7239990234375,
            490.3559875488281,
            292.4519958496094
          ],
          "text": "Nature of Service \nParticulars of Incentives",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            315.0,
            313.823974609375,
            532.2972412109375,
            330.5519714355469
          ],
          "text": "a. Capital Cost: Reimbursement of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            86.58000183105469,
            313.9079895019531,
            299.0173034667969,
            377.5199890136719
          ],
          "text": "i) \nOpening \nof \nand \nmaintaining \ncurrency \nchests \nat \ncenters \nhaving population of less than 1 \nlakh in under banked States",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            315.0,
            329.8680114746094,
            532.2974243164062,
            471.9119873046875
          ],
          "text": "50% of capital expenditure subject \nto a ceiling of ` 50 lakh per \ncurrency chest.  In the North \nEastern region up to 100% of \ncapital expenditure is eligible for \nreimbursement \nsubject \nto \nthe \nceiling of ` 50 lakh. \n \nb. Revenue cost: Reimbursement of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b15",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            337.5,
            471.2279968261719,
            532.2986450195312,
            550.6800537109375
          ],
          "text": "50% of revenue expenditure for the \nfirst 3 years. In the North Eastern \nregion 50% of revenue expenditure \nwill be reimbursed for the first 5 \nyears.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            329.82000732421875,
            560.9639892578125,
            523.057373046875,
            609.1199951171875
          ],
          "text": "a. Exchange of soiled notes – ` 2 \nper packet for exchange of soiled \nnotes up to denomination ` 50",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            85.26000213623047,
            560.9879760742188,
            297.9384765625,
            624.6600341796875
          ],
          "text": "ii) \nExchange \nof \nsoiled \nnotes/ \nadjudication \nof \nmutilated \nbanknotes over the counter at \nbank branches",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b14",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            329.82000732421875,
            619.1640014648438,
            523.0562133789062,
            651.7920532226562
          ],
          "text": "b. \nAdjudication \nof \nmutilated \nnotes – ` 2 per piece",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99429321289062,
            778.7152709960938,
            315.73931884765625,
            806.1103515625
          ],
          "text": "1",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 10.98,
            "name": "Calibri",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "width": 595.4400024414062,
      "height": 841.6799926757812,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            83.94000244140625,
            35.508018493652344,
            537.9373779296875,
            51.600013732910156
          ],
          "text": "iii) \nDistribution of coins over counter i. ` 25 per bag for distribution of coins",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            305.3999938964844,
            51.767967224121094,
            537.9384155273438,
            97.3799819946289
          ],
          "text": "over the counter. \n \nii. The incentives would be paid on the",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            321.6000061035156,
            97.3080062866211,
            537.9373779296875,
            145.01998901367188
          ],
          "text": "basis of withdrawal from currency \nchest, without waiting for claims from \nbanks.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            305.3999938964844,
            162.8279571533203,
            537.9395751953125,
            178.79995727539062
          ],
          "text": "iii. Banks may put in place a system of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            305.3999938964844,
            178.7279815673828,
            537.9397583007812,
            256.0799865722656
          ],
          "text": "checks and balances to ensure that \ncoins are distributed to retail customers \nin small lots and not to bulk customers. \n \niv. The distribution of coins shall be",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            321.6000061035156,
            256.0080261230469,
            537.9384765625,
            319.5599670410156
          ],
          "text": "verified \nby \nRBI \nRegional \nOffices \nthrough inspection of currency chest / \nincognito visits to branches etc.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            340.4519958496094,
            474.21600341796875,
            361.5359802246094
          ],
          "text": "3. \nOperational Guidelines to avail performance-based incentives –",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            373.7279968261719,
            552.3408813476562,
            437.27996826171875
          ],
          "text": "i) \nThe incentives will be paid on the soiled notes actually received in the Issue Office \nof the RBI. Banks need not submit a separate claim in this regard.  Currency chest branch \nwill have to pass on the incentive to the linked branches for the soiled notes tendered by \nthem on a pro-rata basis.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            447.1679992675781,
            552.3396606445312,
            494.8799743652344
          ],
          "text": "ii) \nSimilarly, incentive will be paid in respect of the adjudicated notes received along \nwith the soiled note remittances / sent separately by registered / insured post in a sealed \ncover to the RBI.  No separate claim is required to be made.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            236.57997131347656,
            504.8280334472656,
            387.7559814453125,
            520.800048828125
          ],
          "text": "-------------------------------------",
          "font_info": {
